## 4. Products & Services

- **Detailed descriptions:** Roll-off dumpster rentals (typical fleet 10–40 cubic-yard containers); construction & demolition (C&D) debris removal; residential clean-up / junk removal; commercial waste container solutions. Customers are primarily contractors and construction companies, plus homeowners and commercial accounts.
